text.tspan: Alex is a university student, who also juggles a part-time job, gaining valuable experience. He is a
tech-savvy individual, who is keen on optimizing his electronic device usage. Despite his busy schedule, he
faces a common challenge- a tendency to leave devices powered on when not needed. This also makes
him lack awareness about the environmental risks associated with such habits. Alex is seeking practical
ways to minimize his ecological footprint.
